🚨NWA in the @JacobAndCo “Grande Complication” collection: introducing the jaw dropping Astronomia Green Dragon 🐉 
Housed in the iconic and unmistakable 18k white gold domed case, the mythological creature sculpted in 18K rose gold and hand-painted in green, red and gold colors, it stands atop a base of 202 baguette diamonds totaling more than 8 carats and slithers within the four complications of the iconic Astronomia movement with the double-axis Tourbillon that turning in two axes: one in 60 seconds and the second in 2.5 minutes.

The dragon alone takes up to three months to craft from a solid block of rose gold into this fire-breathing, ruby-eyed, completely hand-crafted serpent.⁣ 
The Astronomia Dragon is a truly unique, groundbreaking timepiece that elevates the art of watchmaking combining the highest level of Swiss timepiece craftsmanship and the horological decorative arts.
Piece Unique

node.text:
To reach those goals you’ve got to be willing to play all the angles meticulously. From the relationship status between @JacobAndCo and Bugatti Rose gold and white diamonds baguette 💎🔥

The case is inspired by the flowing lines of the Chiron and the movement, or “engine block,” intended to duplicate the Bugatti engine, is placed under a massive sapphire crystal, on display for all to see. With the push of right-hand crown of the timepiece the engine comes to life, just like a true internal combustion engine. 
The movement is set with a total of 578 exquisite components. 
Right now Jacob’s workshop is doing something no one has ever even attempted before: to seamlessly combine engines and watches💯

node.text:
Upclose and some photo studio of the new @artisansdegeneve ”Maggiore Challenge✨

Their client was inspired by The Lake Maggiore in Switzerland and wanted to recreate the autumnal season with colors like orange and grey while recalling his childhood memories of the place.

The sapphire dial is enhanced by the rose gold counters, the circular-grained bezel contrats with the rose gold case.

The movement is skeletonized, beveled and polished by hand, some pieces were treated in anthracite for a perfect harmony of colors. 

Artisans de Genève is an independent company specialized in the personalization of timepieces. Artisans de Genève is not affiliated with Rolex SA nor authorized by them to intervene on their products for any reason whatsoever. This personalization was ordered for his private use by a customer who owns a Rolex® timepiece.

In details: the amazing @JacobAndCo Epic SF24 GMT 18K rose gold Flying Tourbillon 🔥
It displays 24 timezones through its patent split Flap display 
Inspired by the traditional boards seen in airports and train stations. You can call it Globetrotter 🙌🏻✈️🚄
Limited Edition of only 101 pieces worldwide
⌚️tag price: 💲210,000.00
